  {*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Features for Border property of TStyleLabel class.
  -------------------------------------------------------------------------------}
  {=------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Características para la propiedad Border de la clase TStyleLabel.
  -------------------------------------------------------------------------------}
